<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='223000' id='t-223000'>But technology moved on, as technology is wont to do.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='226000' id='t-226000'>And slowly, slowly, at the end of the 20th century,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='229000' id='t-229000'>that scarcity started to get eroded --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='231000' id='t-231000'>and I don't mean by digital technology;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='233000' id='t-233000'>I mean by analog technology.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='235000' id='t-235000'>Cassette tapes, video cassette recorders,</span>
