<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='239000' id='t-239000'>created new opportunities</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='241000' id='t-241000'>for us to behave in ways</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='243000' id='t-243000'>that astonished the media business.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='245000' id='t-245000'>Because it turned out</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='247000' id='t-247000'>we're not really couch potatoes.</span>
