<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='282000' id='t-282000'>And so the media industries</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='284000' id='t-284000'>begged, insisted, demanded</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='286000' id='t-286000'>that Congress do something.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='288000' id='t-288000'>And Congress did something.</span>
