<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='541000' id='t-541000'>Because in the end,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='543000' id='t-543000'>the real threat</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='546000' id='t-546000'>to the enactment of PIPA and SOPA</span>
